{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e4b-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1153"},"text":"§ 1153.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Retirement Savings Lost and Found","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e4c-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Establishment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e4d-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than 2 years after ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-29"},"text":"December 29, 2022","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary, in consultation with the Secretary of the Treasury, shall establish an online searchable database (to be managed by the Secretary in accordance with this section) to be known as the “Retirement Savings Lost and Found”. The Retirement Savings Lost and Found shall—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e4e-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/a/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" allow an individual to search for information that enables the individual to locate the administrator of any plan described in paragraph (2) with respect to which the individual is or was a participant or beneficiary, and provide contact information for the administrator of any such plan;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e4f-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/a/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" allow the Secretary to assist such an individual in locating any such plan of the individual; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e50-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/a/1/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" allow the Secretary to make any necessary changes to contact information on record for the administrator based on any changes to the plan due to merger or consolidation of the plan with any other plan, division of the plan into two or more plans, bankruptcy, termination, change in name of the plan, change in name or address of the administrator, or other causes.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e51-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Plans described","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A plan described in this paragraph is a plan to which the vesting standards of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t29/s1053"},"text":"section 1053 of this title","children":[],"tail":" apply."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e52-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Administration","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Retirement Savings Lost and Found established under subsection (a) shall provide individuals described in subsection (a)(1) only with the ability to search for information that enables the individual to locate the administrator and contact information for the administrator of any plan with respect to which the individual is or was a participant or beneficiary, sufficient to allow the individual to locate the individual’s plan in order to make a claim for benefits owing to the individual under the plan.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e53-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Safeguarding participant privacy and security","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In establishing the Retirement Savings Lost and Found under subsection (a), the Secretary, in consultation with the Secretary of the Treasury, shall take all necessary and proper precautions to—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e54-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" ensure that individuals’ plan and personal information maintained by the Retirement Savings Lost and Found is protected; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e55-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" allow any individual to contact the Secretary to opt out of inclusion in the Retirement Savings Lost and Found.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e56-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definition of administrator","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of this section, the term “administrator” has the meaning given such term in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t29/s1002/16/A"},"text":"section 1002(16)(A) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e57-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Information collection from plans","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Effective with respect to plan years beginning after the second December 31 occurring after the date of the enactment of this subsection, the administrator of a plan to which the vesting standards of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t29/s1053"},"text":"section 1053 of this title","children":[],"tail":" apply shall submit to the Secretary, at such time and in such form and manner as is prescribed in regulations—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e58-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the information described in paragraphs (1) through (4) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s6057/b"},"text":"section 6057(b) of title 26","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e59-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the information described in subparagraphs (A) and (B) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s6057/a/2"},"text":"section 6057(a)(2) of title 26","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e5a-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" the name and taxpayer identifying number of each participant or former participant in the plan—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e5b-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" who, during the current plan year or any previous plan year, was reported under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s6057/a/2/C"},"text":"section 6057(a)(2)(C) of title 26","children":[],"tail":", and with respect to whom the benefits described in clause (ii) thereof were fully paid during the plan year;"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e5c-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" with respect to whom any amount was distributed under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s401/a/31/B"},"text":"section 401(a)(31)(B) of title 26","children":[],"tail":" during the plan year; or"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e5d-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e/3/C"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"C"},"text":"(C)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" with respect to whom a deferred annuity contract was distributed during the plan year; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e5e-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" in the case of a participant or former participant to whom paragraph (3) applies—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e5f-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e/4/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" in the case of a participant described in subparagraph (B) thereof, the name and address of the designated trustee or issuer described in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t26/s401/a/31/B/i"},"text":"section 401(a)(31)(B)(i) of title 26","children":[],"tail":" and the account number of the individual retirement plan to which the amount was distributed; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e60-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/e/4/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" in the case of a participant described in subparagraph (C) thereof, the name and address of the issuer of such annuity contract and the contract or certificate number.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e61-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"f"},"text":"(f)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Use of information collected","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e62-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/f/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" may use or disclose information collected under this section only for the purpose described in subsection (a)(1)(B), and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e63-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/f/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" may disclose such information only to such employees of the Department of Labor whose official duties relate to the purpose described in such subsection.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e64-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/g"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"g"},"text":"(g)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Program integrity audit","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"On an annual basis for each of the first 5 years beginning one year after the establishment of the database in subsection (a)(1) and every 5 years thereafter, the Inspector General of the Department of Labor shall—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e65-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/g/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" conduct an audit of the administration of the Retirement Savings Lost and Found; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e66-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c","identifier":"/us/usc/t29/s1153/g/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" submit a report on such audit to the Committee on Health, Education, Labor, and Pensions and the Committee on Finance of the Senate and the Committee on Ways and Means and the Committee on Education and Labor of the House of Representatives.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id5b0a5e67-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/406/tI/s523"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–406, title I, § 523","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/328/dT/tIII/s303/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–328, div. T, title III, § 303(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-29"},"text":"Dec. 29, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/5339"},"text":"136 Stat. 5339","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id5b0a5e68-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id5b0a5e69-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"changeOfName","id":"id5b0a5e6a-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Change of Name","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Committee on Education and Labor of House of Representatives changed to Committee on Education and the Workforce of House of Representatives by House Resolution No. 5, One Hundred Eighteenth Congress, ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2023-01-09"},"text":"Jan. 9, 2023","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
